    "long_instructions": "## Refining and Editing Chat\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to polish and improve the content you generated earlier.\r\n\r\nYour goal is to make your final product clearer, catchier, or more creative—based on your role.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Use AI Chat to revise or enhance the draft you created in the last stage. You might ask:\r\n    - Can you make this shorter, stronger, or more persuasive?\r\n    - Can you make it funnier, more professional, or more inspiring?\r\n    - Here’s what I like—can you keep that but adjust the parts that don’t land?\r\n2. As you refine, update your group slide deck with the stronger version of your content (name + slogan, visuals, script, or jingle).\r\n3. Want better results? Give AI feedback on what didn’t work in the first version and ask for a new take until it feels presentation-ready. ",
